# LiteStartup Skills

Modular AI skill packages for LiteStartup.

## Skill Router

| Skill | Intent | Entry Point |
|-------|--------|-------------|
| publish | publish, sync, write blog/docs/website/changelog, send email, bind repo | `litestartup-skills/publish/SKILL.md` |
| admin | init saas, create project, scaffold, configure, deploy | `litestartup-skills/admin/SKILL.md` |

## File References

- Publish Skill: `litestartup-skills/publish/SKILL.md`
  - Capabilities: `litestartup-skills/publish/capabilities/{bind,sync,email,status}.md`
  - Specs: `litestartup-skills/publish/specs/{docs,blog,website,changelog}.md`
  - Templates: `litestartup-skills/publish/templates/`
- Admin Skill: `litestartup-skills/admin/SKILL.md`
  - Capabilities: `litestartup-skills/admin/capabilities/{init,configure,status}.md`
  - Specs: `litestartup-skills/admin/specs/{env-config,ls-capabilities,features}.md`

## Rules

1. NEVER display API keys (`~/.litestartup/credentials`)
2. Look for `litestartup.yaml` to find the content repo
3. Read the relevant spec BEFORE writing any content
4. For website pages: confirm type (website vs block) with user first
5. After writing: sync per `capabilities/sync.md` (Windows → AI-native API / Linux → script)
